  "obverse": {
    "description": "Half length full armoured bust of King Christian V facing right. The King is wearing a bend with the pendant of the Order of the Elephant.\r\nMain features of this portrait (used only in this type and same design 4 Mark coin) are the bow tie and an elaborated wig.",
